ail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F14102431_10154574734093825_4411300379944126392_n.jpg%3Foh%3Df975b39a8037b8ecfe57f9088e74c1f2%26oe%3D59C80873&h=abe5c717&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/14463059_10154667838423825_7071565382041340311_n.jpg?oh=a826b0967519d2bd8cbff93608e42891&amp;oe=599CC36C\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F14463059_10154667838423825_7071565382041340311_n.jpg%3Foh%3Da826b0967519d2bd8cbff93608e42891%26oe%3D599CC36C&h=5684eb9a&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n又幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n女版陳澤滔"},{"pid":"831bcb4fea2961915de2142000f7450a0ddb42ca","tid":290610,"uid":25055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T21:19:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>熱普城內閧不斷，但係黎黎去去睇毓民鬥雙禿、雙鄭，下下都係男人會有點視覺疲勞。三個組織入面當然要睇下女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，比較下邊面先係美女集中地<br />\n<br />\n首先係熱血公民，全部年過30<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n出場有熱時大媽殘秀慧同個妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/20/093614_48bffc62ff63560befc7fd2ebf1bd5a0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F20%2F093614_48bffc62ff63560befc7fd2ebf1bd5a0.jpg&h=751bfe57&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/20/093616_744240c9abf21ba8e7680c67ba0d3edd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F20%2F093616_744240c9abf21ba8e7680c67ba0d3edd.jpg&h=c98e6a6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n話告鳩神駒但得講字嘅打令<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/20/093756_487925ca88397ad9e4ddd69f862666ce.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F20%2F093756_487925ca88397ad9e4ddd69f862666ce.jpg&h=9ea84950&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後係唯一清泉建築師bonix<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，不過疑似被更生滿玩弄過身體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/20/094035_623a91d05dcc4fff44af7d653926e94e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F20%2F094035_623a91d05dcc4fff44af7d653926e94e.jpg&h=0ee0f12d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n城邦派係復康會，傻人集中地、跟隨得個癲佬都唔會正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/20/094434_9619a5d0f6a0965f391783c39e6a2c84.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F20%2F094434_9619a5d0f6a0965f391783c39e6a2c84.jpg&h=cdae1603&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/20/094439_efae77a85c7b5d25d9791728b0982484.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F20%2F094439_efae77a85c7b5d25d9791728b0982484.jpg&h=3bc3aa75&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/20/094444_31ee9cbc9c7b94d020894a926f6cb0bd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F20%2F094444_31ee9cbc9c7b94d020894a926f6cb0bd.jpg&h=8d3fc221&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n普羅就毓民有號召力，搵女，揀女有一手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/20/094621_01b5cffa5338becea2fab6d694ae5f88.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F20%2F094621_01b5cffa5338becea2fab6d694ae5f88.jpg&h=f3cd9c21&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/20/094624_05b2925c9cccfc87fa0584859860f05e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F20%2F094624_05b2925c9cccfc87fa0584859860f05e.jpg&h=52e7e207&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知各位巴打鍾意邊派入面嘅囡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最底個張右二<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n求ig <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"618c96eeb7bc4ccc5293034d6f36c4cc8fdac989","tid":290610,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T03:12:45.000Z","msg":"究竟咩節目可以睇到毓民班西施？係咪要收費嗰啲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9425f086ce1e4cb5daae0fda1c84a422a8b7b7c5","tid":290610,"uid":38665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T03:56:39.000Z","msg":"話說vega tam呢條女企邊邊架？"}]}